Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... damn caterpillar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chore boy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:02:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if hundreds of\Nweapons are built in,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he can be defeated by someone\Nwith a spear of blind determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that kid doesn't have any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a survival instinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or does he not fear death\Nbecause he has faith in himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where you die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My Mighty Battle Spear is...\NWhat the hell did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave it five punches.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's it for your spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined the Mighty\NBattle Spear would be broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's taken that many explosions.\NHis body can't keep up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Conclusion Of The Deadly Battle!\NA Spear Of Blind Determination!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Prepare yourself...\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a big enough foothold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a foothold this size,\NI can kick your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the spear blade broken,\Nthat's just a bomb on a stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power is cut by half.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb on a stick? So what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the shape you're in, it's more\Nthan enough force to blow you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your body falling apart like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whatever you say\Nsounds like just a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it up!\NThe moment you defied me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you signed your death warrant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die! Bleah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh ooh ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He keeps hopping around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:05:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many built-in\Nweapons does he have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's that?!\N--Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a ton of arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, chore boy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your punches are powerless\Nagainst this wootz Steel Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even make a dent in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Pistol!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How impudent!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless! Useless! How useless!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This armor won't break, even with\Nhundreds of monkey punches!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm pretty close...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen. The ultimate force\Nmeans the strongest equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the strongest power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:07:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strong one is the one\Nwho survives. The strong one is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that'll be me! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless! Useless! It's useless!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even pride will only get you so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good. This is all you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The strongest\Narmor is cracking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too late.\NYou're done for, anchor boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:08:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trap! Get out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chore boy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a survival instinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or does he not fear death\Nbecause he has faith in himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Gum-Gum...\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All right!!\N--Good job!!\N--You're the best, chore boy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get carried away, brat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! He's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you escape?! It's a steel net!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Below us is the ocean.\NThe game is over, anchor boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's\Ngetting the last laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! That's our Don!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Make him fall!\N--Get him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can get my arms and legs out,\Nthe game is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't he flinch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why does he go that far?\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna end it... for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant Gavel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant Gavel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don Krieg...\N--Don... Don was defeated! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dammit! Why? Why was Don...\N--All right, chore boy!!\N--Good job!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He really did it!!\N--A-Amazing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this real? This is Don Krieg\Nwe're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So strong! He's too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What's all this fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You've come to!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lost! Your Don lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to daydream,\Ngo save that kid already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--He won't be floating up to the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those with the Devil Fruit power\Nare hated by the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lose the ability to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say, you damn geezer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me that sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do if it's too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:13:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hang in there!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wouldn't die, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your faith, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, these guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:14:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should give up his ambition\Nrather than dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be easy...\Nto give up your ambition, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...\NI don't know why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I withdrew even a step,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like those various\Nimportant things such as pledges
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and promises in the\Npast will be shattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I won't be able to come\Nback to where I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can be defeated by someone\Nwith a spear of blind determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know an idiot who's holding back\Nthat spear for a stupid reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All... Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, chore boy! Don't you die on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don! What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was Don...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Krieg has been defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be true...\NHe's the ruler of the East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is...\NThat man is... That man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say so...\NJust take a look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His proud armor got shattered\Nand he's knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got defeated good.\NYou're not gonna see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the only man I admired...\NI believed he was the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey wait, underling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you move around now,\Nthe poison'll pass into your system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't move around!\NI'm saying this for your own good!\N--Hey! You're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chore boy! Don't die! Can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have things to do, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't die! Chore boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:17:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say... Say something!!\NChore boy! Don't die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're really something else...\N--I'm the strongest!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win! No one defeats my force!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold him! He's not even conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll win!!\N--Please stop, Don!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win! Using my force!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... have to win!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:18:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the strongest man!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Krieg... We lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's withdraw gracefully\Nand start afresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything, Sanji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Don't ever come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san, when he wakes up,\Nplease tell him I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll see you again in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about it carefully,\Nthat's the only thing I want to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Don Krieg's ambition\Nbecame mine as well before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... I can live only\Na few more hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of stupid that I'm resolved\Nbecause I don't have much time left,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this time, I want to do it with\Nmy own will... in my own way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, there'll be nowhere\Nfor me to escape, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with loyalty towards Don!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just been running away using\NDon Krieg's name as a shield...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're resolved,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't have to think\Nabout stupid things
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like fearing your enemy\Nor how to keep from getting hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned it from that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Patty! Carne!! Give him the boat\Nused to go grocery shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to\Ngive our boat to pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gonna happen to our\Ngrocery shopping?! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! Let those guys swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just bring it out already!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay, we got it...\N--Don't yell at us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, we'll bring it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I hesitate?\NWhat was I so worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about it, I feel stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then! We gratefully\Naccept the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to return it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. If you have the courage\Nto come here to return it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,try it, you small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! Just keep this in your brain!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the sea restaurant\NBaratie, where cooks fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.19,0:21:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! What a scary restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.17,0:22:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were nice guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.17,0:22:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they'll let me join them\Nagain when I see them next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.69,0:22:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll be able\Nto see them again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.69,0:22:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be free...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:23:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm free from the chores\Nsince pops promised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right.\N--By the way, will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.15,0:24:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going. I won't become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you haven't given up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.98,0:24:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm hoping to go to\Nthe Grand Line some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.99,0:24:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the right time yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.99,0:24:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Set Sail! The Seafaring\NCook Sets Off With Luffy"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.99,0:24:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
